{"type": "article", "id": 30408, "title": "极简架子", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-01T23:05:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160801203659VO9SvuEieNqfFZWn.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>想要创造独特的视觉效果并不一定需要特别复杂的设计，这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/32458529/Field\" rel=\"nofollow\">Field</a> 的极简架子就是一个典型的案例。它由来自乌克兰的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Dimas1c\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dmitry Kozinenko</a> 设计，我们曾经介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29376.html\">海胆柜</a>也是他的作品。整个架子由黑色或白色的金属框架构成，Kozinenko 在当中对五处金属管进行了弯折处理，可以作为搁板放上物品。从正面远远看去物品就好像是漂浮在空中一样，走近后又像是一个神奇的金属瀑布。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801205904hdQS5ozJ4a7xbHTK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801205907VfBrzMUHdtgFYSCR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801205907mqReYELvV6QMscdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801205909w6f7SUmLGOh8dYg3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}